msgstr "(мала назву «Велика Риба» у Ератосфена та Арата грецькою)"

#. type: Content of: <p><table><tr><td>
#: ../../skycultures/greek_leidenAratea/description.en.utf8:270
msgid ""
"It is so darkly drawn here that you would not recognise it in the stars. "
"That is why the colours have been dipped into a blue-green scheme instead of"
" the original red-purple one."
